        "Description": "Good morning 47\r\rYour targets are the remaining members of The Royal Flush, all operatives of Blue Blood. Ruby Red is trying to overthrow the bank, while Madame Kenyon wants to open a new account for something called &apos;Operation Epsilon&apos;. FInding out more about this operation could lead us to the Inquisitor. Laree Parrish is the leader of this operation in New York. Make sure the camera&apos;s don&apos;t spot you, so that Blue Blood doesn&apos;t know what we are doing.\r\rGood luck 47",
